<plot>An impatient nurse who cares for a sick old woman dislikes her work. The old woman asks hands the nurse an old photo album of her life. The nurse reads looks at the photo album and sees the old woman as a teenager, a bride, a mother, a grandmother, and a widow. The nurse realizes that this old lady she has been assigned to is a beautiful human being and that life is too short not to treasure.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?410530</url></doc>
